# ✅ Java To-Do List (with File Storage)

A terminal-based task manager that supports adding and removing tasks, and saves them in a file so you never lose your list.

---

## ✨ Features

- 📝 Add and remove tasks via command line
- 💾 Saves tasks in a local file (`tasks.txt`)
- 🔁 Loads saved tasks on startup
- 🧠 Validates user input
- ❌ Graceful error handling

---

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
javac TodoApp.java
java TodoApp
